author: remyroy
content: EthStaker is hosting the Holesky Pectra Upgrade Livestream (<t:1740432600:f>) on YouTube (<https://www.youtube.com/live/XfdDV0RhDyI>). We are looking for someone to join the call and explain the key EIPs or changes included in Pectra. It would be a ~10 minutes segment. Let us know if you are interested.
